  "description": [
    "Page Six GADSDEN COUNTY TIMES ESTABLISHED 1901 Published each Thursday at 221223 E Washington Street Quincy Florida by QUINCY PUBLISHING COMPANY C C Nicolet Editor Bntered in the post office at Quincy Florida under the Act of March 5 1879 as matter of the second class Oae years2oo School Band Scores a Hit The Gadsden County High School Band in its first for mal indoor concert last Friday did itself proud The program quite properly in view of the circumstances was selected more from the standpoint of showing how the band could meet every type of music than on a basis of classical standards And the boys and girls of both junior and senior bands came through in splendid fashion The senior band had been heard before in open air con certs and at football games where the programs were limited to elementary marches and patriotic music The junior band was making its debut Both of them not only left parents and fond aunts and uncles happy but also wowed the gen eral public The kind of a concert that often is merely a bore that has to be attended turned out to be a keen musical experience The senior"
